<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="just-adv">just <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dʒʌst/    美 /dʒʌst/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-exactly">1.★ <strong>正好；恰好 (exactly)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>just then</strong> / just at that time 
就在那时</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The summer here is <strong>just as</strong> hot as it is in my hometown<strong>as_2</strong>
这里的夏天和我家乡的夏天一样热。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was <strong>just about to</strong> go out <strong>when</strong> it began to rain.
他刚要出去，天就下起了雨。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You <strong>just have to</strong> accept things and get on with your life.
你只好接受这些事情，继续你的生活。</p><footer>2008 山东</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>刚刚；刚才：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Where is Eric? 
艾瑞克在哪儿？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— He has just gone / just went out.
他刚刚出去/刚才出去了。</p></div>

<h4 id="3-only-simply">3.★ <strong>只是；仅仅 (only / simply)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>just a minute / moment / second</strong> 
等一会儿</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I decided to learn French, <strong>just for fun</strong>. 
我决定学习法语，只是为了消遣。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Just because</strong> a subject is difficult to learn, <strong>it does not mean</strong> you are not good at it.
不要因为某一科目难学，就认为你学不好。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>非常；真正：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The chocolate is just wonderful. 
巧克力非常好吃。</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.<strong>请；尽管：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Anytime you want me, just send for me. 
无论什么时候需要，只管派人来叫我。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="just-about">just about</h3>
<p>1.<strong>几乎；差不多：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Some people will do just about anything to save money.
为了省钱，有的人几乎愿意做任何事情。</p><footer>2013 全国</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li><strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (正如) a single word can change the meaning of a sentence, a single sentence can change the meaning of a paragraph.  （2015 浙江改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. Just as  </p></div>